rComments: This was a really interesting class and not particularly difficult. A kind and understanding prof. Gives about 10% away for free, exams were not hard and they were marked leniently. However, the presentations were what brought everyone's marks down as he and the TA marked everyone a bit more harshly than expected. Overall I would recommend it.
Easiest A+ I ever took! Very interesting topics learned and course structure!
